Class MyStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • elevator.MyStack
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElevatorStack

    public class MyStack
extends java.lang.Object
    Custom Stack class that will be used to hold ElevatorPerson Objects. The stack uses an Array implementation.
    Author:
    Wesley Chan
